MiniGameEventDetector - Class in com.worldbiomusic.minigameworld.minigameframes.helpers
Event detector to send Minigames

[IMPORTANT]
Detectable event means can get player from "Default event list" or "Detailed event list"

[Default Event List]
- PlayerEvent
- EntityEvent
- HangingEvent
- InventoryEvent
- InventoryMoveItemEvent
- PlayerLeashEntityEvent

[Detailed Event list]
- MiniGameEventDetector.getPlayersFromBlockEvent(org.bukkit.event.block.BlockEvent, java.util.List<org.bukkit.entity.Player>)
- MiniGameEventDetector.getPlayersFromEntityEvent(org.bukkit.event.entity.EntityEvent, java.util.List<org.bukkit.entity.Player>)
- MiniGameEventDetector.getPlayersFromVehicleEvent(org.bukkit.event.vehicle.VehicleEvent, java.util.List<org.bukkit.entity.Player>)
- MiniGameEventDetector.getPlayersFromUnknownCommandEvent(org.bukkit.event.command.UnknownCommandEvent, java.util.List<org.bukkit.entity.Player>)
